text: Gustav Max Wiederkehr (2 October 1905 – 7 July 1972) was a Swiss football administrator. He was the President of UEFA from 1962 to 1972.Historisches Lexikon der SchweizLa asamblea de la Copa de Ferias == References == Category:1905 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Presidents of UEFA Category:People from Zürich
